{"tid":1433981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚文召組]唔該做多啲關於警犬誠信嘅文宣","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T18:46:45.000Z","uid":53481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4cfd2678a4a7e0bfa6d54e09b03f4255f76c662a","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"發覺宜家有關警犬嘅文宣工作<br />\n好多只係point to point咁駁警犬<br />\n外界可能只會覺得警犬同示威者你一言我一語，不分勝負<br />\n如果可以抽高啲層次，一次過攻警犬嘅誠信破產，其實咁樣好好多<br />\n材料都有唔少啦，例如有線啱啱先篤爆警犬北角嘅部署講大話<br />\n<br />\n宜家需要嘅，係整出嚟，做文宣！文宣！文宣！<br />\n幫手整整有關警犬無誠信嘅文宣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00366a9bbe28b4bf5dc39ccba88121d26dc58a64","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"我唔識IT，如果唔係我自己都做咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到文宣組見到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e9c6f304f00c745c6ee79b8105a9c1465ac19b","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:49:41.000Z","msg":"推到文宣組見到為止"},{"pid":"98a086705839101ea9deb6b4845d3f6721e3f388","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15c089d8e9db77e15102bb47acf3c59ff5c87db3","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac4baa1244ee811fe16cb8cabf3e8d14db36201a","tid":1433981,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply